{"tid":724392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"M永遠在N前面, 麥包比先係PSG大佬","createTime":"2018-07-01T01:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T03:22:55.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9fa423d829556786e2a52d03bd162645aa8a9a9","tid":724392,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"完爆尼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbcb7ea8a55cfddb4c776274b256bcb5c77e6c2","tid":724392,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410d7e88f37619c2592263a9906f0782177a9096","tid":724392,"uid":17481,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁卡雲尼咪大大佬 K係M前面喎"},{"pid":"2acf6dc8807863815f3435af9d51644f085ca57b","tid":724392,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410d7e88f37619c2592263a9906f0782177a9096","tid":724392,"uid":17481,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁卡雲尼咪大大佬 K係M前面喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"你依家先知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1a714367461a0643622c43bea8363ba935ecb4","tid":724392,"uid":156106,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿發表聲明，指尼馬獲准豁免操練，將在日內赴巴黎聖日耳門體檢，料以破世界轉會費紀錄2.22億歐元（約20.55億港元）轉戰法甲。尼馬在加泰羅尼亞市機場接受了法國Nineup報獨家專訪，透露無法上位成為一哥，是他決定離開球會的主因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040749_d50608616a9827d73c08791473884943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040749_d50608616a9827d73c08791473884943.jpg&h=a7aba570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「巴塞有一名老大哥，他決定球會用那個領隊、購入那些球員、踢甚麼陣式和那位球員正選，我們總活在陰影之下。」沒有指名道姓，尼馬卻娓娓道出有人這些年來幾乎主宰了球會所有決策。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬回憶上月與老大哥的對話：「記得上個月跟他在酒吧聊天，談起球會來季目標，我預告自己今年將會大爆發，為球會重奪聯賽和歐聯。」<br />\n<br />\n「老大哥沒有回應，望著酒杯問我：『你知道英文字母的順序嗎？』我說當然知道，然後他就說：『N永遠排在M後面，這是定律，即使你成功，亦是在我的允許之下。』」<br />\n<br />\n「瞬間我明白了他意思了，他要永遠當球會的老大哥。於是我不忿地回應了一句：『那麼C排在M的前面又代表甚麼呢？』他馬上就黑面了，自此我們就沒有再說過話。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040958_df7985dfc89d5fe7151dbd8d7595a3b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040958_df7985dfc89d5fe7151dbd8d7595a3b9.png&h=2761de48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時助手催促上機，尼馬最後向記者道：「我要起程往巴黎了，你還有甚麼問題嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n記者：「沒有了，剛好口袋有一包M&amp;M朱古力，送給你上機吃吧。」<br />\n<br />\n尼馬接過朱古力後苦笑：「看吧，連朱古力也是只有M沒有N，他媽的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040809_0f87c64f7679ff9b2802c30ae8eb3d59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040809_0f87c64f7679ff9b2802c30ae8eb3d59.png&h=b309b031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f523999b044d5d61962f62631029ad62dbf77ed","tid":724392,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"nineup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw WOW"},{"pid":"1700176724ae39a966ba52901c5d9a7d92fba8be","tid":724392,"uid":35547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"410d7e88f37619c2592263a9906f0782177a9096","tid":724392,"uid":17481,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁卡雲尼咪大大佬 K係M前面喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"卡雲尼c字開頭啊忽然球迷"},{"pid":"f7125f6d1dac42f978587670f7fced98fe72a7c5","tid":724392,"uid":17481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1700176724ae39a966ba52901c5d9a7d92fba8be","tid":724392,"uid":35547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"410d7e88f37619c2592263a9906f0782177a9096","tid":724392,"uid":1